ing: 1 (6 ounce) package DOLEÂ® Tender Garden Blend
2 oranges, peeled and cut in half slices
1 fennel bulb, trimmed, cored and thinly sliced lengthwise
8 pitted Kalamata olives, cut in half
des: "Salty kalamata olives balance the sweet orange in this salad. The tangy orange vinaigrette brings it all together."
ins: Combine salad, oranges, fennel and olives in large bowl. Toss with Fresh Orange Dressing, to coat, as desired. Refrigerate any remaining vinaigrette.
